Depew St. #9 , Denver, CO 80227', 'Rent: $1050 + $45 utility', 'Bedrooms: 2', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Available: MID August 2022!!', 'Type: Apartment', 'Comfortable 1 bedroom!', 'Great Location!', 'On the bus line', 'Wellington Plaza Apartments are located with lovely views of the Rocky Mountain Landscape just to the west.', "Located right off Jewell and Sheridan it's within walking distance of King Soopers, several restaurants and some shopping.", 'There is a bus stop right out front for you to easily get to where you need to go.', 'The apartments feature inviting, comfortable living spaces all at an affordable price.', 'Come enjoy the convenience of living at the Wellington Plaza apartments and apply today!', 'show contact info', 'No Pets.', '*', "***We are looking for a tenant with previous rental history and verifiable income around 2.5x's the rent.", 'We also check credit and criminal history.', 'If there is an issue in any area you may be required to pay a larger deposit.', 'The application fee is $40 per adult.', '****', 'INCO Property Management & Sales', 'Leasing Department', '6640 S Broadway Suite A', 'Centennial, CO 80121', 'View Website: <URL>']
